code: @Override protected Result<Influencer> map(SearchHit hit) {     BytesReference source = hit.getSourceRef().     try (InputStream stream = source.streamInput().         XContentParser parser = XContentFactory.xContent(XContentType.JSON).createParser(NamedXContentRegistry.EMPTY, LoggingDeprecationHandler.INSTANCE, stream)) {         Influencer influencer = Influencer.LENIENT_PARSER.apply(parser, null).         return new Result<>(hit.getIndex(), influencer).     } catch (IOException e) {         throw new ElasticsearchParseException("failed to parser influencer", e).     } }
